name: Artist of the Rocking New Year JACKPOT Event!
description:
Thank you so much for joining in the Hic Et Nunc Community Event. Hope it was a great experience for you all!  

This NFT is NOT part of the jackpot and will not be listed in the Event shop.  However, all proceeds will be used to transfer the Jackpot to the winner and/or for future HEN Community events.

Leftovers will be burned following the closure of sales for this event on January 3rd.
